{"tid":726564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已有兩妻大馬41歲男子　再娶11歲女童","createTime":"2018-07-02T13:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T21:24:36.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1efab8ab721ed8aa3989c2eb6b9bc40f5c57248c","tid":726564,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:33:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">已有兩妻大馬41歲男子　再娶11歲女童</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞吉蘭丹州一名已有兩名妻子的41歲男子，再迎娶11歲女孩，惹起廣泛爭議，有兒童權益組織促請關注大馬童婚問題。大馬副首相旺阿茲莎稱，已派出官員會見女童母親，將就調查報告決定進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n該名男子是一間清真寺住持，也是一名橡膠商人。他有兩名妻子、6名孩子，最大的已有16歲。他的一名妻子上周在網絡「祝賀」丈夫迎娶11歲女孩瑪絲，還附有相片，令事件引起注意。大馬傳媒引述一名關注兒童權益的社工稱，瑪絲的家人是割橡膠工人，男子瞞着妻子，6月在泰國與瑪絲結婚。<br />\n<br />\n吉蘭丹州伊斯蘭事務局稱，若取得伊斯蘭法庭的許可，與18歲以下少女結婚，是伊斯蘭教允許的。不過，除了取得法庭的許可，也須取得女方家長的同意。若該男子未有取得許可，將面臨6個月監禁。<br />\n<br />\n大馬人權組織稱，該國有1.6萬名15歲以下女童已婚，促請改革法律來終止童婚。兒童權益人士賽義德（Syed Azmi Alhabshi）說：「娶11歲女童為妻，形同是戀童癖的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n（星洲日報/法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180701/s00005/1530451678975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180701%2Fs00005%2F1530451678975&d=RmGgjlo2L4VoqaZYwsVXVzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=bf8e6a5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180701%2Fs00005%2F1530451678975&h=981e4a91\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180701/s00005/1530451678975</a>"},{"pid":"11acce78497d2471b9c6922ad1580b6646b87b4b","tid":726564,"uid":11962,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教真係邪教黎"},{"pid":"f61cd420a8d9040ebc27353b605b21466c6e2aa4","tid":726564,"uid":21917,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"11acce78497d2471b9c6922ad1580b6646b87b4b","tid":726564,"uid":11962,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教真係邪教黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"仲要法律容許  痴撚線"},{"pid":"33f2d635b830c10805ab8156a70dfa4e147277aa","tid":726564,"uid":156542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"11歲就要西部大開發"},{"pid":"6cb5e271ce8f75d6a4cfa085ede60a0ebe6eb69d","tid":726564,"uid":38465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33f2d635b830c10805ab8156a70dfa4e147277aa","tid":726564,"uid":156542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"11歲就要西部大開發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:37:39.000Z","msg":"搵處女真係要幼稚園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11歲就容許結婚cls"},{"pid":"f2a82d409d10cc56f7b53e099b167909c8907dff","tid":726564,"uid":122212,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:38:19.000Z","msg":"呢個世界咩人都有架啦<br />\n有乜咁出其<br />\n係又反唔係又反<br />\n唔撚抵得人地有女食???"},{"pid":"522989f917addd33f2dfdf6d0ad7e27f491c05a1","tid":726564,"uid":45213,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DaNCfDLW0AAP5E5?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDaNCfDLW0AAP5E5%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=b48e448d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41e78a3a8bfafd6db4773e30f1c2855d0a2e445c","tid":726564,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"522989f917addd33f2dfdf6d0ad7e27f491c05a1","tid":726564,"uid":45213,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DaNCfDLW0AAP5E5?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDaNCfDLW0AAP5E5%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=b48e448d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid